title: Arizona U.S. House 4th District Results: Paul Gosar Wins
title_page: Arizona U.S. House 4th District Results: Paul Gosar Wins – Election Results 2016 – The New York Times
text:
Representative Paul Gosar won the United States House of Representatives 4th District race in Arizona on Tuesday. Gosar is up by 43 points with all precincts reporting.
Below are detailed results for the race. View other Arizona election results on our full Arizona results page. See all races on our House map.
